   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Avina Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As the focal point of the VAC Alliance in Brazil, Avina facilitates the construction of good governance of the Voices for Climate Action Program in Brazil, where it works with WWF-Brazil, Hivos and SSN (in alliance with IIEB). These efforts involve the articulation of the permanent dialogue between the allied organizations, the sharing of strategic decisions and co-responsibility in the elaboration of the demands inherent to the implementation of the Program in Brazil, which ensures the systematic alignment between the member organizations on the fundamental issues of existence of the program, in relation to collaborative management and process methodologies.
It assumes a strategic role as a catalyst agent for all efforts of member organizations to maintain co-construction and coordination among them, as the focal point of the alliance in Brazil.</narrative>
  </description>
